# Antidote+ frontend — copy to `.env` (or `.env.local`) if you need to override.
#
# Base URL of the backend API.
#   Dev  : leave EMPTY — requests stay relative (/api/…) and use the Vite proxy
#          to http://localhost:8000 (see vite.config.js).
#   APK / static host: there is no proxy, so set this to your hosted backend,
#          e.g. https://api.antidote.example
# If this is wrong on a device, the AI calls silently fall back to safe defaults
# (Gemini identification/summaries appear to do nothing).
VITE_API_BASE=
